Package: com.github.amkay.gradle.git.release.notes.task

[Groovy] Class ExtractReleaseNotesFromCommitLogTask

        • com.github.amkay.gradle.git.release.notes.task.ExtractReleaseNotesFromCommitLogTask

        • This is the main Task of this plugin. It searches for the Git tag matching the current version of the project the plugin is applied on, extracts all commit messages between the current HEAD and the found Git tag, filters and cleans them based on the configuration given in GitReleaseNotesPluginExtension and writes the results into the configured Markdown file.
